prodNameC: 免疫特2500 胰島素樣生長因數-I
ingredientsDesc:
IGF-I Bead Pack
coated with monoclonal murine anti-IGF-I.
IGF-I Reagent Wedge
11.5 mL alkaline phosphatase (bovine calf intestine) conjugated to polyclonal rabbit anti-IGF-I, in buffer.
IGF-I Adjustors
Two vials (Low and High), 4 mL each, of IGF-I in a protein/buffer matrix.
IGF-I Sample Diluent
20 mL of concentrated IGF-I-free buffer matrix.
